{"tid":1402862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到今日黑警濫權濫暴亂打市民亂拉人,做整合,加大宣傳罷工","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:52:55.000Z","uid":47905,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ef810be9c5ee02c81c2a1d173da4849828e927","tid":1402862,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"近期黑警濫權濫暴已經唔只係遊行示威<br />\n已經去到各區各地<br />\n唔舉旗出催淚彈,亂打亂拉普通市民<br />\n黑警已經去到一個無法律可以制止既地步<br />\n<br />\n應該要整一個整合版,有齊晒所有黑警濫權濫暴亂打市民<br />\n加大宣傳8月5罷工<br />\n肯定會更多市民響應<br />\n<br />\n而且香港人真係需要開一個記者會<br />\n係各區代表咁樣<br />\n表明香港黑警已經全面失控"},{"pid":"5f6924fb58f78b91f2536a9de0128d34dcc9f21f","tid":1402862,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:09:05.000Z","msg":"今日要整合真係有排整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由警車有人換黑衫開始"},{"pid":"9c747c87db09fe5c8dbca59d919119597ff10923","tid":1402862,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f6924fb58f78b91f2536a9de0128d34dcc9f21f","tid":1402862,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:09:05.000Z","msg":"今日要整合真係有排整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由警車有人換黑衫開始"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"今日真係好多<br />\n<br />\n但就係因為咁<br />\n肯定好多人嬲<br />\n會罷工<br />\n<br />\n睇黃大仙咁多人出就知"},{"pid":"dd46898928c48fe1c24f5903cf579e38ad2dbc85","tid":1402862,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97650269ad35db23f0cba1049c006dd3701412ea","tid":1402862,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd8223e605270a89a69fa82e9484ea3d9601455","tid":1402862,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:29:15.000